# Cursor / Copilot Rules

When working in this project always follow these rules:

## Before writing any code
1. Read PROMPT.md — understand what you are building
2. Read API.md — know every endpoint and data shape
3. Read DOMAIN_RULES.md — never break business rules
4. Read SCREENS.md — understand each page's behaviour
5. Read COMPONENTS.md — follow the component structure
6. Read DESIGN_SYSTEM.md — use only defined tokens and styles
7. Read ERROR_HANDLING.md — handle every error case correctly

## Code style
- Functional components only, no class components
- useState + useEffect for all data fetching (no extra libs)
- One useEffect per data concern per page
- Extract repeated fetch logic into the api/ modules, never inline fetch calls in JSX
- All CSS goes in src/styles/ or as a dedicated .css file per component — no inline styles except for truly dynamic values (e.g. a width calculated from JS)
- Use CSS class names from DESIGN_SYSTEM.md — do not invent new class names without adding them to the design system

## Never do
- Never use Tailwind, Bootstrap, MUI, Chakra, or any CSS framework
- Never use axios — use the client.js fetch wrapper
- Never use React Query — plain hooks only
- Never hardcode error messages — always use response.message from API
- Never show a 409 or 422 error as a Toast — use ConflictBanner
- Never allow form submission while loading/submitting is true
- Never display LAB slot as user-selectable
- Never submit a LAB entry with fewer than 3 groups

## File creation order (when building from scratch)
1. src/styles/tokens.css
2. src/styles/global.css
3. src/api/client.js
4. src/api/*.js  (one per entity)
5. src/components/Spinner.jsx
6. src/components/Toast.jsx
7. src/components/ConflictBanner.jsx
8. src/components/Sidebar.jsx
9. src/components/StatCard.jsx
10. src/components/DataTable.jsx
11. src/components/EntityDrawer.jsx
12. src/components/TimetableGrid.jsx
13. src/components/EntryForm.jsx
14. src/pages/Dashboard.jsx
15. src/pages/MasterData.jsx
16. src/pages/Assignments.jsx
17. src/pages/TimetableBuilder.jsx
18. src/pages/TimetableViews.jsx
19. src/App.jsx
20. src/main.jsx
21. index.html (add Google Fonts link tag)

## How to start the project
```bash
npm create vite@latest timetable-frontend -- --template react
cd timetable-frontend
npm install react-router-dom
npm run dev
```

No other dependencies are needed or allowed.
